={
  "from": "The Ink Connect Team <hello@inkconnect.app>",
  "to": "{{ $('trigger_webhook_onboarding').item.json.body.email }}",
  "subject": "You're in. Here's what to do first.",
  "html": "<h2>Welcome to Ink Connect, {{ $('trigger_webhook_onboarding').item.json.body.firstName }}!</h2><p>Your profile at <strong>{{ $('trigger_webhook_onboarding').item.json.body.shopName }}</strong> is ready. Here's how to hit the ground running:</p><ol><li><strong>Complete your profile</strong> — add bio, specialties, and location</li><li><strong>Upload 5+ portfolio images</strong> — AI will analyze your style</li><li><strong>Check open requests</strong> — clients are already looking for artists like you</li></ol><p><a href='{{ $env.APP_BASE_URL }}/artist-dashboard' style='background:#000;color:#fff;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;'>Get Started</a></p><p style='color:#666;font-size:12px;'>Unsubscribe from these emails: <a href='{{ $env.APP_BASE_URL }}/unsubscribe?email={{ $('trigger_webhook_onboarding').item.json.body.email }}'>here</a></p>"
}

={
  "from": "The Ink Connect Team <hello@inkconnect.app>",
  "to": "{{ $('trigger_webhook_onboarding').item.json.body.email }}",
  "subject": "Clients are looking at your profile right now",
  "html": "<h2>Your profile is getting views</h2><p>Here are a few tips to convert profile visitors into clients:</p><ul><li><strong>Add your city and state</strong> so local clients can find you</li><li><strong>Post your best work</strong> — quality beats quantity</li><li><strong>Write a compelling bio</strong> that tells your story</li></ul><p><a href='{{ $env.APP_BASE_URL }}/artist-dashboard' style='background:#000;color:#fff;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;'>Polish Your Profile</a></p><p style='color:#666;font-size:12px;'><a href='{{ $env.APP_BASE_URL }}/unsubscribe?email={{ $('trigger_webhook_onboarding').item.json.body.email }}'>Unsubscribe</a></p>"
}

={
  "from": "The Ink Connect Team <hello@inkconnect.app>",
  "to": "{{ $('trigger_webhook_onboarding').item.json.body.email }}",
  "subject": "8 open requests match your style",
  "html": "<h2>Clients are waiting for you</h2><p>There are open tattoo requests on Ink Connect that match your style. Paid artists can bid directly — clients see your proposal, portfolio, and price. No cold outreach needed.</p><p><a href='{{ $env.APP_BASE_URL }}/requests' style='background:#000;color:#fff;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;'>Browse Open Requests</a></p><p style='color:#666;font-size:12px;'><a href='{{ $env.APP_BASE_URL }}/unsubscribe?email={{ $('trigger_webhook_onboarding').item.json.body.email }}'>Unsubscribe</a></p>"
}

={
  "from": "The Ink Connect Team <hello@inkconnect.app>",
  "to": "{{ $('trigger_webhook_onboarding').item.json.body.email }}",
  "subject": "What happens after you send a bid",
  "html": "<h2>How the bidding process works</h2><ol><li>You browse open requests and submit a bid with your price, message, and availability</li><li>The client reviews all bids and their portfolios</li><li>If they choose you, they accept your bid — you both get connected</li><li>A deposit secures the appointment</li></ol><p>It's that simple. Paid subscribers get unlimited bids and AI-powered bid drafts.</p><p><a href='{{ $env.APP_BASE_URL }}/pricing' style='background:#000;color:#fff;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;'>Upgrade to Bid</a></p><p style='color:#666;font-size:12px;'><a href='{{ $env.APP_BASE_URL }}/unsubscribe?email={{ $('trigger_webhook_onboarding').item.json.body.email }}'>Unsubscribe</a></p>"
}

={
  "from": "The Ink Connect Team <hello@inkconnect.app>",
  "to": "{{ $('trigger_webhook_onboarding').item.json.body.email }}",
  "subject": "Your Founding Artist perks expire in 4 days",
  "html": "<h2>Don't miss your locked-in rate</h2><p>Your 180-day Founding Artist trial is progressing. When it ends, you lock in the $19/mo rate forever — that's 35% off the standard price.</p><p>Founding Artists also get:</p><ul><li>Founding Artist badge on your profile</li><li>Search priority boost over free-tier artists</li><li>Unlimited bids and AI bid drafts</li></ul><p><a href='{{ $env.APP_BASE_URL }}/pricing' style='background:#000;color:#fff;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;'>View Founding Artist Perks</a></p><p style='color:#666;font-size:12px;'><a href='{{ $env.APP_BASE_URL }}/unsubscribe?email={{ $('trigger_webhook_onboarding').item.json.body.email }}'>Unsubscribe</a></p>"
}

={
  "from": "The Ink Connect Team <hello@inkconnect.app>",
  "to": "{{ $('trigger_webhook_onboarding').item.json.body.email }}",
  "subject": "One step away from going live",
  "html": "<h2>You're almost there, {{ $('trigger_webhook_onboarding').item.json.body.firstName }}</h2><p>Your profile is set up — now it's time to start winning clients. Here's your final checklist:</p><ul><li>✅ Profile complete with bio and specialties</li><li>✅ 5+ portfolio images uploaded</li><li>✅ Location set so local clients can find you</li><li>⬜ Submit your first bid on an open request</li></ul><p><a href='{{ $env.APP_BASE_URL }}/requests' style='background:#000;color:#fff;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;'>Find Your First Client</a></p><p style='color:#666;font-size:12px;'><a href='{{ $env.APP_BASE_URL }}/unsubscribe?email={{ $('trigger_webhook_onboarding').item.json.body.email }}'>Unsubscribe</a></p>"
}
